---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Security Awareness Training | Coro Cybersecurity — Blue Cap IT" description="Coro security awareness training educates your employees with engaging training modules and simulated phishing campaigns. Turn your team into your first line of defense.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="cybersecurity.html">Cybersecurity</a> <span>/</span> Security Awareness Training</div>
      <div class="section-label">Coro Cybersecurity</div>
      <h1>Security Awareness <span class="grad">Training</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Your employees are your biggest security asset — or your biggest vulnerability. Coro's security awareness training turns your team into a human firewall with engaging training and realistic phishing simulations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Security Awareness Training</div>
          <h2>Your Team Is Your <span class="grad">First Line of Defense</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Technology can block most threats — but the ones that get through rely on human error. A single employee clicking a phishing link can compromise your entire organization. Coro's training program builds a security-conscious culture that dramatically reduces this risk.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">Blue Cap IT sets up your training program, customizes phishing simulations, and tracks employee progress — so you can see your organization getting stronger over time.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Train Your Team</a>
            <a href="cybersecurity.html" class="btn-ghost">View All Coro Modules</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:graduation-cap" /></div>
            <div><h4>Engaging Training Modules</h4><p>Short, interactive courses covering phishing, password security, social engineering, data handling, and more. Designed to be completed in minutes, not hours.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:fish" /></div>
            <div><h4>Phishing Simulations</h4><p>Realistic simulated phishing emails test your employees in real-world conditions. Identify who needs additional training before a real attack happens.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:bar-chart-3" /></div>
            <div><h4>Progress Tracking</h4><p>Dashboards show completion rates, phishing simulation results, and risk scores for every employee and department.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:refresh-cw" /></div>
            <div><h4>Continuous Learning</h4><p>Training isn't a one-time event. Automated campaigns deliver ongoing education and regular phishing tests to maintain awareness year-round.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Key Capabilities</div>
        <h2>What Coro Training <span class="grad">Includes</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:graduation-cap" /></div>
          <h3>Training Library</h3>
          <p>A full library of interactive training modules covering phishing, social engineering, password hygiene, data handling, physical security, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:fish" /></div>
          <h3>Phishing Simulations</h3>
          <p>Customizable simulated phishing campaigns that mimic real-world attacks. Test employees with emails that look like they come from common services and vendors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:trending-up" /></div>
          <h3>Risk Scoring</h3>
          <p>Each employee gets a risk score based on training completion and phishing simulation performance. Identify your highest-risk users at a glance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:bell" /></div>
          <h3>Automated Campaigns</h3>
          <p>Set up recurring training assignments and phishing simulations that run automatically. New employees are enrolled in onboarding training immediately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:clipboard-list" /></div>
          <h3>Compliance Reporting</h3>
          <p>Generate reports showing training completion rates and phishing simulation results. Demonstrate security awareness compliance to auditors and leadership.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:trophy" /></div>
          <h3>Micro-Learning</h3>
          <p>When an employee fails a phishing simulation, they immediately receive a short, targeted training module on what they missed — turning mistakes into learning moments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Build a Security Culture</div>
    <h2>Get Coro Security Training<br/><span class="grad">from Blue Cap IT</span></h2>
    <p>Contact us to start a security awareness training program for your team. We'll set up training modules, launch phishing simulations, and track your organization's progress.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
